    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1949-09-18T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1949-09-18T00:00:00-05:00" n="1108"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1108">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">393.115/9–1849: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul at Shanghai</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">McConaughy</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Shanghai</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-09-18">September 18,
                            1949</date>.<lb/>[Received September 18—5:01 a. m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>3911. SS <hi rend="italic">Flying Clipper</hi> from Taku Bar arrived Shanghai
                    September 18, made fast Hongkew-Shanghai wharf 1345 hours. <hi rend="italic"
                        >Flying Independent</hi> from Hong Kong made fast same wharf 1435 hours.
                    Previous message from master to agent stated <hi rend="italic">Independent</hi>
                    stopped by Chinese naval craft at mouth Yangtze 1630 local time then given
                    permission proceed. <hi rend="italic">Clipper</hi> arrived shortly after and
                    proceeded up Yangtze passing <hi rend="italic">Independent</hi> en route. <hi
                        rend="italic">Clipper</hi> apparently cleared also by Chinese naval vessel
                    but no wireless report from master received.</p>
                <p>These first American vessels arrive Shanghai since port closure June 25. Great
                    local interest.</p>
                <p>Repeated CNO for information. Please pass VOANY.<note n="71" xml:id="d1108fn71"
                        >Voice of America, New York.</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">McConaughy</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
